- [https://cs.uwaterloo.ca/~thachisu/survival.pdf Graduate Study Survival Guide] by Toshiya Hachisuka @UWaterloo
- [http://karpathy.github.io/2016/09/07/phd/ A Survival Guide to a PhD] by Andrej Karpathy @Tesla
- [https://xinmingtu.cn/blog/2022/Academic-resource/ Collection of some resources related to the PhD journey] by Xinming Tu @UW

