- [https://www.di.ens.fr/~fbach/learning_theory_class/ Learning Theory from First Principles] by Francis Bach @INRIA 
- [https://csml.princeton.edu/bridgingmathematicaloptimizationslidesvideos Bridging Mathematical Optimization, Information Theory, and Data Science] @Princeton University 
